@echo off\necho Attempting to repair network connection...\n\n:: Release and Renew IP Address\nipconfig /release\nipconfig /renew\n\n:: Clear DNS Client Resolver Cache\nipconfig /flushdns\n\n:: Reset Winsock Catalog\nnetsh winsock reset\n\n:: Restart DHCP Client Service (optional)\nnet stop dhcp\nnet start dhcp\n\necho Network repair completed. Please check your network connection.